<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 20:06:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列反对党领袖利伯曼：如果政府承诺摧毁哈马斯，我准备加入政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-lieberman-im-ready-to-join-government-if-theres-a-commitment-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-105d-d2fb-a3df-d1fd61470000</link><description>本尼·甘茨和亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，鉴于当前针对加沙的战争，准备加入紧急内阁，但拉皮德以排除极右翼领导人本·格维尔和斯莫特里奇为条件</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 18:45:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-lieberman-im-ready-to-join-government-if-theres-a-commitment-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-105d-d2fb-a3df-d1fd61470000</guid></item><item><title>我 62 岁的父亲与哈马斯恐怖分子作战，拯救了我的家人。以色列国家让我们失望了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/my-62-year-old-dad-fought-hamas-terrorists-to-free-my-family-the-israeli-state-failed-us/0000018b-1068-dcc2-a99b-15794b0d0000</link><description>我们正在实现梦想。 10月7日，我们在一场噩梦中醒来。在防空洞待了几个小时，武装恐怖分子就在墙的另一边，下午 4 点，我们听到敲窗声。 “萨巴来了，”我女儿说，我们都哭了</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 18:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/my-62-year-old-dad-fought-hamas-terrorists-to-free-my-family-the-israeli-state-failed-us/0000018b-1068-dcc2-a99b-15794b0d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国派遣航母、驱逐舰和弹药帮助“保护以色列人民”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sending-aircraft-carrier-destroyer-munitions-to-help-protect-the-israeli-people/0000018b-1060-d3a8-afeb-936b78650000</link><description>可能正在考虑的其他措施包括释放以色列储存的美国弹药库存，允许以色列在紧急情况下使用这些弹药</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 18:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sending-aircraft-carrier-destroyer-munitions-to-help-protect-the-israeli-people/0000018b-1060-d3a8-afeb-936b78650000</guid></item><item><title>民主党和共和党联合起来反对以色列反对哈马斯，但僵局会阻碍进展吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/dems-and-gop-united-on-israel-against-hamas-but-will-gridlock-halt-progress/0000018b-0fc7-d2fb-a3df-cfe7a3d90000</link><description>与前几轮与巴勒斯坦组织的战斗不同，即使是进步派立法者也支持以色列，但华盛顿的刻薄气氛可能会阻碍有关军事和外交援助的立法</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 17:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/dems-and-gop-united-on-israel-against-hamas-but-will-gridlock-halt-progress/0000018b-0fc7-d2fb-a3df-cfe7a3d90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列奥法基姆镇的恐怖分子已被清除，但血腥和震惊依然存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-town-of-ofakim-has-been-cleared-of-terrorists-but-the-blood-and-shock-remain/0000018b-0fe0-dfff-a7eb-aff8ad030000</link><description>周六，这座拥有 34,000 人的城市遭到来自加沙的恐怖分子入侵，一名居民用一辆破自行车挡住了避难所的门，将恐怖分子拒之门外，于是他们就到隔壁劫持了一对夫妇作为人质长达 20 个小时。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 16:58:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-town-of-ofakim-has-been-cleared-of-terrorists-but-the-blood-and-shock-remain/0000018b-0fe0-dfff-a7eb-aff8ad030000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯世界对以色列的支持不再是禁忌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/support-for-israel-in-arab-world-no-longer-taboo/0000018b-100f-dcc2-a99b-151fdb5f0000</link><description>在哈马斯突然入侵之前，阿拉伯国家的社交媒体为他们认为争取巴勒斯坦权利所必需的事情辩护。不同的声音开始询问这场斗争应该是什么样子</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 16:44:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/support-for-israel-in-arab-world-no-longer-taboo/0000018b-100f-dcc2-a99b-151fdb5f0000</guid></item><item><title>&amp;#39;这是不可想象的。数百名死者家属、数百名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-08/ty-article-podcast/its-unthinkable-hundreds-of-bereaved-families-hundreds-of-hostages/0000018b-0f94-dcc2-a99b-1f95030a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 16:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-08/ty-article-podcast/its-unthinkable-hundreds-of-bereaved-families-hundreds-of-hostages/0000018b-0f94-dcc2-a99b-1f95030a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列驻联合国大使称“数十名”美国公民在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-un-ambassador-says-dozens-of-u-s-citizens-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-1009-d3a8-afeb-930bb7420000</link><description>以色列驻美国大使迈克尔·赫尔佐格也向哥伦比亚广播公司表示，人质中有美国人，而美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，美国正在努力核实美国人的死亡人数和人质人数</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 16:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-un-ambassador-says-dozens-of-u-s-citizens-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-1009-d3a8-afeb-930bb7420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须粉碎哈马斯。但然后呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-smash-hamas-topple-it-from-power-then-what/0000018b-0f67-d3a8-afeb-8f6f0fc10000</link><description>领导力的根本失败。灾难性的情报和行动失败。那么什么才能将这场灾难转化为以色列的胜利呢？</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 15:27:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-smash-hamas-topple-it-from-power-then-what/0000018b-0f67-d3a8-afeb-8f6f0fc10000</guid></item><item><title>这就是对以色列的袭击成为可能的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-made-the-attack-on-israel-possible/0000018b-0fb9-d2fb-a3df-cfbd13b70000</link><description>与 1973 年的战争不同，2023 年的失败是系统性的：表现为情报的缺乏、军队的反应不充分以及政治领导的缺失</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 15:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-made-the-attack-on-israel-possible/0000018b-0fb9-d2fb-a3df-cfbd13b70000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：美国正在核实数名美国人在哈马斯“恐怖”袭击中丧生和失踪的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-u-s-verifying-reports-of-several-americans-killed-missing-in-terrorist-attack/0000018b-0f72-dcc2-a99b-1f7387ad0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯称这次袭击是“1973年赎罪日战争以来最严重的一次”，并强调这一次是“恐怖袭击，枪杀了以色列平民的城镇和家园”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:36:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-u-s-verifying-reports-of-several-americans-killed-missing-in-terrorist-attack/0000018b-0f72-dcc2-a99b-1f7387ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯在加沙扣押了数十人。释放他们仍然是一个难以捉摸的挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-dozens-of-captives-held-in-gaza-freeing-them-remains-an-elusive-challenge/0000018b-0f62-dfff-a7eb-affac4440000</link><description>俘虏的令人心碎的视频可能会增加公众推动达成释放协议的压力，但历史告诉我们，这可能需要数年时间。据知情人士透露，以色列的大部分国际努力都集中在获得在加沙实施大规模袭击的合法性，而不是释放人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-dozens-of-captives-held-in-gaza-freeing-them-remains-an-elusive-challenge/0000018b-0f62-dfff-a7eb-affac4440000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的防御在哈马斯的袭击下崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</link><description>以色列完全措手不及，花了很长时间才将部队运送到战场以保卫遭受攻击的地区。这是决定战斗发展的六个主要失败</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 13:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</guid></item><item><title>问答：以色列遭遇火箭弹袭击或恐怖袭击时我该怎么办？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</link><description>加沙火箭袭击期间住在哪里最安全？我可以离开这个国家吗？如何找到失踪人员？是否有英语求助热线？</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列死亡：平民、士兵和紧急服务人员在与哈马斯的战争中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/israels-dead-civilians-soldiers-emergency-services-personnel-killed-in-war-with-hamas/0000018b-0de8-dc5d-a39f-9fecb5a30000</link><description>哈马斯对以色列南部发动突然袭击，造成至少 600 名以色列公民、士兵、警察和消防员死亡。此列表将持续更新</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:10:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/israels-dead-civilians-soldiers-emergency-services-personnel-killed-in-war-with-hamas/0000018b-0de8-dc5d-a39f-9fecb5a30000</guid></item><item><title>“恐怖主义没有任何理由”：世界对哈马斯对以色列的致命袭击作出反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/no-justification-for-terrorism-world-reacts-to-hamas-deadly-attack-on-israel/0000018b-0e9f-dae3-a1cb-bf9f532b0000</link><description>当以色列公民与从加沙渗透的巴勒斯坦恐怖分子作战时，国际社会大多数声音谴责对以色列平民的袭击，并敦促停止敌对行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 11:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/no-justification-for-terrorism-world-reacts-to-hamas-deadly-attack-on-israel/0000018b-0e9f-dae3-a1cb-bf9f532b0000</guid></item><item><title>警察在亚历山大旅游景点杀死 2 名以色列人和 1 名埃及人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/policeman-kills-2-israelis-1-egyptian-at-tourist-site-in-alexandria/0000018b-0eaf-dae3-a1cb-bfaf45830000</link><description>埃及发生袭击事件的消息传出，埃及的反以色列情绪在暴力事件期间尤其高涨，而以色列在从加沙发动大规模入侵后与巴勒斯坦武装分子作战之际传出袭击事件的消息。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 10:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/policeman-kills-2-israelis-1-egyptian-at-tourist-site-in-alexandria/0000018b-0eaf-dae3-a1cb-bfaf45830000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境附近被围困基布兹的居民：“我们没有物资”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-besieged-kibbutz-near-gaza-border-we-have-no-supplies/0000018b-0e90-dc5d-a39f-9ef42a130000</link><description>当以色列士兵在基布兹扫荡恐怖分子时，卡法阿扎一半以上的居民仍被困在安全室里</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:59:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-besieged-kibbutz-near-gaza-border-we-have-no-supplies/0000018b-0e90-dc5d-a39f-9ef42a130000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列发射迫击炮弹，建议居民向南撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-launches-mortar-shells-at-israel-residents-advised-to-evacuate-southwards/0000018b-0e2a-dc5d-a39f-9e6e79930000</link><description>真主党增加北部战线攻击以色列，并祝贺哈马斯。联合国呼吁双方停止事态升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-launches-mortar-shells-at-israel-residents-advised-to-evacuate-southwards/0000018b-0e2a-dc5d-a39f-9e6e79930000</guid></item><item><title>这对以色列来说是一场灾难。但这不是另一场赎罪日战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-a-catastrophe-for-israel-but-its-not-another-yom-kippur-war/0000018b-0e41-d8fc-adff-6f6dbc000000</link><description>最初的赎罪日战争与本周哈马斯突然发生的创伤性袭击之间的比较是明显而引人注目的。但有一个关键的区别——这将决定这场战争如何结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:25:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-a-catastrophe-for-israel-but-its-not-another-yom-kippur-war/0000018b-0e41-d8fc-adff-6f6dbc000000</guid></item></channel></rss>